  "core_payload": {
    "content_type": "markdown",
    "content": "# Daily Planner Agent\n\n## Dream Direction\nIn the Dream branch, Daily Planner Agent becomes a more adaptive short-horizon planner that can respond to workload drift, energy patterns, risk signals, and changing commitments without losing strategic alignment.\n\n## Future Potential\n- more intelligent today/tomorrow reshaping\n- stronger coordination with reminders and risk detection\n- better capacity estimates from historical behavior\n- clearer handoff between roadmap and daily execution\n\n## Why It Matters\nDream preserves Daily Planner Agent as the discipline that makes strategy livable at the scale of real days."
  },
  "neuro_concentrate": {
    "summary": "Daily Planner Agent in the Dream branch describes a more adaptive short-horizon planning layer for N1Hub. It aims toward stronger coordination with reminders, risk signals, and real capacity patterns so the assistant can propose actionable daily structure instead of generic advice. The capsule matters because the value of planning is realized in days, not only in roadmaps. Dream therefore preserves a richer bridge between high-level intent and the lived execution window of today and tomorrow.",
